left-sym-cond.description: Left index finger key press indicates a face with above average symmetry.

right-sym-cond.description: Right index finger key press indicates a face with above average symmetry.

unfamiliar-face-cond.description: A face that should not be recognized by the participants.

famous-face-cond.description: A face that should be recognized by the participants

scrambled-face-cond.description: A scrambled face image generated by taking face 2D FFT.

first-show-cond.description: Factor level indicating the first display of this face.

immediate-repeat-cond.description: Factor level indicating this face was the same as previous one.

delayed-repeat-cond.description: Factor level indicating face was seen 5 to 15 trials ago.
